Application: Airlock Smoke
  Description: End-to-end runtime preview for the termin-airlock-provider CSR shell path. Renders the cosmic-orb custom-namespace contract via the Using override, exercising the v0.9.3 provider dispatch end-to-end through termin-server's CSR shell path. Pair with airlock_smoke.deploy.json. The .termin source itself is generic (no Airlock product content); the React component renders pure aesthetic geometry from termin-airlock-provider.
